rComments: Professor Andre Braen is extremely educated in Maritime Law. He makes you read most of his writings. However, doing his readings are important, especially for the final. His take-home is easier than you think, but he is a tough grader. He prepares you well for maritime law practice and teaches the essentials. This class is interesting.
